<!DOCTYPE html>
<!-- saved from url=(0192)file:///C:/Users/ssunn/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/chatbot0605_merge/proposal/%EC%95%84%EA%B8%B0%EB%8F%8C%EB%B4%84_%EC%95%B1_%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8_%EA%B8%B0%ED%9A%8D%EC%84%9C.html -->
<html lang="ko"><head><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">

<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>아기돌봄 앱 프로젝트 기획서</title>
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500;700&family=Noto+Serif+KR:wght@400;700&display=swap');

  :root {
    --orange: #FF8C42;
    --orange-light: #FFE0CC;
    --orange-mid: #FFBD96;
    --green: #8BC44A;
    --green-light: #E2F0CC;
    --green-mid: #C2E08A;
    --cream: #FFFDF8;
    --gray-50: #FAFAF8;
    --gray-100: #F0EFE8;
    --gray-200: #D8D6CC;
    --gray-400: #9E9B8E;
    --gray-600: #5E5B50;
    --gray-800: #2E2C26;
    --blue: #4A8FC4;
    --blue-light: #DCF0FF;
    --purple: #8B6FCA;
    --purple-light: #EDE8F8;
    --red: #E05A5A;
    --red-light: #FDEAEA;
    --teal: #3DADA0;
    --teal-light: #D8F4F1;
    --radius-sm: 8px;
    --radius-md: 12px;
    --radius-lg: 20px;
    --shadow-sm: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    --shadow-md: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  body {
    font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
    background: var(--cream);
    color: var(--gray-800);
    line-height: 1.75;
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  /* ── COVER ── */
  .cover {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFF5ED 0%, #F0FAEE 50%, #FFF5ED 100%);
    padding: 80px 60px 60px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-100);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .cover::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -60px; right: -60px;
    width: 320px; height: 320px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--orange-light) 0%, transparent 70%);
    opacity: 0.5;
  }
  .cover::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -80px; left: -40px;
    width: 260px; height: 260px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--green-light) 0%, transparent 70%);
    opacity: 0.5;
  }
  .cover-inner { position: relative; z-index: 1; max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .cover-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--orange);
    color: white;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 5px 14px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .cover h1 {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
    font-size: 40px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.25;
    color: var(--gray-800);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .cover h1 span { color: var(--orange); }
  .cover-subtitle {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--gray-600);
    font-weight: 300;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }
  .cover-meta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 32px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .cover-meta-item { font-size: 13px; color: var(--gray-400); }
  .cover-meta-item strong { display: block; color: var(--gray-600); font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px; }

  /* ── LAYOUT ── */
  .container { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 40px; }

  /* ── NAV ── */
  .toc {
    background: var(--gray-50);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-100);
    padding: 24px 40px;
  }
  .toc-inner { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .toc-title { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: var(--gray-400); text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .toc-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
    list-style: none;
  }
  .toc-list a {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--gray-600);
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    border: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
    background: white;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .toc-list a:hover { border-color: var(--orange); color: var(--orange); }

  /* ── SECTIONS ── */
  section { padding: 60px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-100); }
  section:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .section-header { margin-bottom: 36px; }
  .section-number {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: var(--orange);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--gray-800);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }
  .section-desc {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--gray-600);
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  h3 { font-size: 17px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--gray-800); margin: 28px 0 12px; }
  h4 { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--gray-600); margin: 16px 0 8px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
  p { margin-bottom: 12px; color: var(--gray-600); }

  /* ── CARDS ── */
  .card {
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid var(--gray-100);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 24px 28px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }
  .card + .card { margin-top: 16px; }

  .card-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .card-grid-3 {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 16px;
  }

  /* ── FEATURE CARDS ── */
  .feature-card {
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid var(--gray-100);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: 20px 22px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .feature-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0;
    width: 4px; height: 100%;
    border-radius: 4px 0 0 4px;
  }
  .feature-card.orange::before { background: var(--orange); }
  .feature-card.green::before { background: var(--green); }
  .feature-card.blue::before { background: var(--blue); }
  .feature-card.purple::before { background: var(--purple); }
  .feature-card.teal::before { background: var(--teal); }
  .feature-card.red::before { background: var(--red); }

  .feature-icon {
    width: 40px; height: 40px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .feature-icon.orange { background: var(--orange-light); }
  .feature-icon.green { background: var(--green-light); }
  .feature-icon.blue { background: var(--blue-light); }
  .feature-icon.purple { background: var(--purple-light); }
  .feature-icon.teal { background: var(--teal-light); }
  .feature-icon.red { background: var(--red-light); }

  .feature-card h3 { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; margin: 0 0 8px; color: var(--gray-800); }
  .feature-card p { font-size: 13px; color: var(--gray-400); margin: 0; }
  .feature-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 3px 10px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    margin-top: 10px;
  }
  .feature-tag.must { background: var(--orange-light); color: var(--orange); }
  .feature-tag.native { background: var(--green-light); color: var(--green); }
  .feature-tag.ext { background: var(--blue-light); color: var(--blue); }

  /* ── TECH STACK ── */
  .tech-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-size: 14px;
  }
  .tech-table th {
    background: var(--gray-50);
    padding: 12px 16px;
    text-align: left;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--gray-400);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--gray-100);
  }
  .tech-table td {
    padding: 14px 16px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-100);
    vertical-align: top;
  }
  .tech-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
  .tech-table tr:hover td { background: var(--gray-50); }

  .tech-name {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--gray-800);
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  .tech-value {
    color: var(--orange);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
  }
  .tech-why { font-size: 13px; color: var(--gray-600); }
  .tech-difficulty {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 3px 10px;
    border-radius: 100px;
  }
  .tech-difficulty.easy { background: var(--green-light); color: #4A8A1A; }
  .tech-difficulty.mid { background: var(--orange-light); color: var(--orange); }
  .tech-difficulty.hard { background: var(--red-light); color: var(--red); }

  /* ── INFO BOX ── */
  .info-box {
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: 18px 20px;
    margin: 16px 0;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .info-box .icon { font-size: 20px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }
  .info-box p { margin: 0; font-size: 14px; }
  .info-box.tip { background: var(--blue-light); border-color: #B8DEFF; }
  .info-box.warn { background: #FFF8E6; border-color: #FFE8A3; }
  .info-box.success { background: var(--green-light); border-color: #C0E08A; }
  .info-box.danger { background: var(--red-light); border-color: #F5BBBB; }

  /* ── PHASE TIMELINE ── */
  .timeline { position: relative; padding-left: 32px; }
  .timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 8px; top: 12px; bottom: 12px;
    width: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--orange), var(--green));
  }
  .timeline-item { position: relative; margin-bottom: 32px; }
  .timeline-dot {
    position: absolute;
    left: -28px; top: 8px;
    width: 16px; height: 16px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 3px solid white;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--orange);
    background: var(--orange);
  }
  .timeline-dot.green { background: var(--green); box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--green); }
  .timeline-dot.teal { background: var(--teal); box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--teal); }
  .timeline-dot.blue { background: var(--blue); box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--blue); }

  .timeline-header {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .timeline-phase {
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700;
    padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 100px;
  }
  .timeline-phase.p1 { background: var(--orange-light); color: var(--orange); }
  .timeline-phase.p2 { background: var(--green-light); color: #4A8A1A; }
  .timeline-phase.p3 { background: var(--teal-light); color: var(--teal); }
  .timeline-phase.p4 { background: var(--blue-light); color: var(--blue); }
  .timeline-title { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--gray-800); }
  .timeline-duration { font-size: 12px; color: var(--gray-400); margin-left: auto; }
  .timeline-tasks {
    display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; margin-top: 10px;
  }
  .task-chip {
    font-size: 12px;
    background: var(--gray-50);
    border: 1px solid var(--gray-100);
    color: var(--gray-600);
    padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: 100px;
  }

  /* ── SCREEN MOCKUP ── */
  .screen-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 12px;
    margin: 24px 0;
  }
  .screen-item {
    background: var(--gray-800);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    overflow: hidden;
    aspect-ratio: 9/16;
    position: relative;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }
  .screen-bar {
    height: 6px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--orange), var(--green));
  }
  .screen-top {
    padding: 10px 10px 6px;
    background: white;
  }
  .screen-title { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--gray-800); }
  .screen-sub { font-size: 8px; color: var(--gray-400); }
  .screen-body { padding: 8px 10px; }
  .screen-card {
    background: var(--gray-50);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 6px 8px;
    margin-bottom: 5px;
  }
  .screen-card-title { font-size: 8px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--gray-600); }
  .screen-card-val { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--gray-800); }
  .screen-label { font-size: 9px; color: var(--gray-400); margin-top: 2px; text-align: center; }

  /* ── DESIGN SYSTEM ── */
  .color-grid {
    display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin: 16px 0;
  }
  .color-swatch {
    width: 64px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    overflow: hidden;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .color-swatch .swatch { height: 48px; }
  .color-swatch .swatch-name { font-size: 11px; color: var(--gray-400); margin-top: 4px; }
  .color-swatch .swatch-hex { font-size: 10px; color: var(--gray-400); font-family: monospace; }

  /* ── USER FLOW ── */
  .flow-step {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0;
    margin: 16px 0;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .flow-box {
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    padding: 10px 16px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--gray-700, var(--gray-800));
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .flow-box.accent { background: var(--orange-light); border-color: var(--orange-mid); color: var(--orange); }
  .flow-arrow {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--gray-200);
    margin: 0 6px;
  }

  /* ── BUDGET ── */
  .budget-bar {
    background: var(--gray-100);
    border-radius: 100px;
    height: 10px;
    margin: 4px 0 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .budget-fill { height: 100%; border-radius: 100px; }
  .budget-row { margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .budget-label { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 2px; }
  .budget-label span:first-child { color: var(--gray-600); }
  .budget-label span:last-child { font-weight: 600; color: var(--gray-800); }

  /* ── API KEY BOX ── */
  .api-box {
    background: var(--gray-800);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: 20px 24px;
    font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #D8D6CC;
    margin: 12px 0;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  .api-box .comment { color: #6E6C60; }
  .api-box .key { color: #F4A623; }
  .api-box .val { color: #8BCA4A; }
  .api-box .str { color: #FF8C42; }

  /* ── PRINT ── */
  @media print {
    body { background: white; }
    .cover { padding: 60px 40px 40px; }
    section { padding: 40px 0; }
  }

  /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .cover { padding: 48px 24px 40px; }
    .cover h1 { font-size: 28px; }
    .container { padding: 0 20px; }
    .toc { padding: 16px 20px; }
    .card-grid, .card-grid-3, .screen-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .cover-meta { gap: 20px; }
  }

  .divider {
    width: 48px; height: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--orange), var(--green));
    border-radius: 2px;
    margin: 12px 0 28px;
  }

  table.simple { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 14px; margin: 12px 0; }
  table.simple th { background: var(--orange-light); color: var(--gray-800); font-weight: 600; padding: 10px 14px; text-align: left; }
  table.simple td { padding: 10px 14px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-100); color: var(--gray-600); }
  table.simple tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }

  .tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 3px 10px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    margin: 2px;
  }
  .tag.orange { background: var(--orange-light); color: var(--orange); }
  .tag.green { background: var(--green-light); color: #3A7A10; }
  .tag.blue { background: var(--blue-light); color: var(--blue); }
  .tag.purple { background: var(--purple-light); color: var(--purple); }
  .tag.gray { background: var(--gray-100); color: var(--gray-600); }

  footer {
    background: var(--gray-800);
    color: var(--gray-400);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 32px 40px;
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  footer strong { color: var(--orange); }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ==============================
     COVER
============================== -->
<div class="cover">
  <div class="cover-inner">
    <div class="cover-badge">Project Planning Document v1.0</div>
    <h1>🍊 <span>아기돌봄</span> 웹앱<br>프로젝트 기획서</h1>
    <p class="cover-subtitle">일상 육아를 스마트하게 — 기록 · 알람 · 발달 · 챗봇 올인원 모바일 웹앱</p>
    <div class="cover-meta">
      <div class="cover-meta-item">
        <strong>프로젝트 유형</strong>
        모바일 우선 반응형 웹앱
      </div>
      <div class="cover-meta-item">
        <strong>타겟 사용자</strong>
        영·유아 부모 (0~24개월)
      </div>
      <div class="cover-meta-item">
        <strong>예상 개발 기간</strong>
        16~20주 (4~5개월)
      </div>
      <div class="cover-meta-item">
        <strong>플랫폼</strong>
        모바일 웹 (PWA)
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- TOC -->
<div class="toc">
  <div class="toc-inner">
    <div class="toc-title">목차</div>
    <ul class="toc-list">
      <li><a href="file:///C:/Users/ssunn/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/chatbot0605_merge/proposal/%EC%95%84%EA%B8%B0%EB%8F%8C%EB%B4%84_%EC%95%B1_%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8_%EA%B8%B0%ED%9A%8D%EC%84%9C.html#overview">01 프로젝트 개요</a></li>
      <li><a href="file:///C:/Users/ssunn/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/chatbot0605_merge/proposal/%EC%95%84%EA%B8%B0%EB%8F%8C%EB%B4%84_%EC%95%B1_%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8_%EA%B8%B0%ED%9A%8D%EC%84%9C.html#tech">02 기술 스택 추천</a></li>
      <li><a href="file:///C:/Users/ssunn/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/chatbot0605_merge/proposal/%EC%95%84%EA%B8%B0%EB%8F%8C%EB%B4%84_%EC%95%B1_%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8_%EA%B8%B0%ED%9A%8D%EC%84%9C.html#features">03 주요 기능 정의</a></li>
      <li><a href="file:///C:/Users/ssunn/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/chatbot0605_merge/proposal/%EC%95%84%EA%B8%B0%EB%8F%8C%EB%B4%84_%EC%95%B1_%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8_%EA%B8%B0%ED%9A%8D%EC%84%9C.html#architecture">04 앱 구조 &amp; 화면 설계</a></li>
      <li><a href="file:///C:/Users/ssunn/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/chatbot0605_merge/proposal/%EC%95%84%EA%B8%B0%EB%8F%8C%EB%B4%84_%EC%95%B1_%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8_%EA%B8%B0%ED%9A%8D%EC%84%9C.html#design">05 디자인 시스템</a></li>
      <li><a href="file:///C:/Users/ssunn/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/chatbot0605_merge/proposal/%EC%95%84%EA%B8%B0%EB%8F%8C%EB%B4%84_%EC%95%B1_%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8_%EA%B8%B0%ED%9A%8D%EC%84%9C.html#integrations">06 외부 연동 상세</a></li>
      <li><a href="file:///C:/Users/ssunn/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/chatbot0605_merge/proposal/%EC%95%84%EA%B8%B0%EB%8F%8C%EB%B4%84_%EC%95%B1_%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8_%EA%B8%B0%ED%9A%8D%EC%84%9C.html#data">07 데이터 구조</a></li>
